{"tid":837030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"返左一次大陸，原來香港冇進步過..香港人幾時先醒？","createTime":"2018-09-26T05:27:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T06:20:45.000Z","uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"56b860878609a463bb97f706faa6d782eb09d82b","tid":837030,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T05:27:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/132734_a36d9c927b860dde42578dec8460e3b7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F132734_a36d9c927b860dde42578dec8460e3b7.png&h=9df66a54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n轉貼"},{"pid":"d0d40c0a926230b28680326ca02ade78ed8ad222","tid":837030,"uid":163350,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T05:28:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cdc5f002b2cbd1427ed82edbcd0dc54942c761a3","tid":837030,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T05:34:23.000Z","msg":"中國香港<br />\n你想點進步"},{"pid":"97e61ce117d317598bf49e74e488c10732fe230e","tid":837030,"uid":38523,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T05:36:10.000Z","msg":"踩港狗又來了<br />\n進步？<br />\n睇過<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">福氣來</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">住屋住到生癌真係世界首創<br />\n搵幾多隻奶波魔魔上踩港都冇用<br />\n</span></span><br />\n奶波魔魔家屬示意圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/08/103744_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F08%2F103744_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=45c1f1e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n［有線中國組］內地租盤甲醛超標 租戶入住兩月患白血病 三日後身亡</span></span><br />\n<br />\n國內最大長租公寓營運商自如早前被指推高北京房租後，再陷入甲醛超標的風波。<br />\n<br />\n一名阿里巴巴員工5月初搬入自如在杭州出租的房間，兩個月後確診患上白血病，接著在短短三日後去世。妻子到他生前住所進行空氣檢測，發現屋內多處甲醛濃度超標，懷疑同死因有關。<br />\n<br />\n消息一出，紛紛有自如租戶在自己單位進行測試，發現甲醛超標不是個別例子；更有受甲醛超標影響的自如租戶退租後，發現自如將有問題單位再出租。<br />\n<br />\n自如一方面發聲明強調所有裝修材料和家具等都符合國家標準，但又同時在全國收回所有首次出租的租盤。他們表示會在百分百檢測合格後，才重新出租；亦會向6月1日後，入住首次出租盤的租戶提供空氣檢測服務。若證實有超標問題，可無條件退租和換租。<br />\n<br />\n本身隸屬鏈家集團的自如靠著收樓、裝修再轉租出去的盈利模式，迅速發展起來。到了今時今日，業務遍布包括北上廣深在內的九個城市，擁有超70萬個租盤，租戶達160萬人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你以為你個仔係學校就安全？<br />\n食飯生癌問你怕未？<br />\n要咁大間屋有咩用？<br />\n子孫都死晒啦</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/23/121700_c746f8a8454559ff71f77c11a5b5b9b4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F23%2F121700_c746f8a8454559ff71f77c11a5b5b9b4.png&h=b9dd422e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/23/121612_7b2a9130f8f96265ba7cf96b5de87a98.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F23%2F121612_7b2a9130f8f96265ba7cf96b5de87a98.png&h=873b6ceb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/23/121618_54d086507e41e7313c69be010a5a47b9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F23%2F121618_54d086507e41e7313c69be010a5a47b9.png&h=94f0ca06&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/23/121624_7bc4e4810a81ea6957189363c68b6d0b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F23%2F121624_7bc4e4810a81ea6957189363c68b6d0b.png&h=52905015&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/23/121634_dda3b64ee6009d40b10debf475181f5f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F23%2F121634_dda3b64ee6009d40b10debf475181f5f.png&h=f2ad668a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n你以為死左就有得安樂？<br />\n推火葬強挖棺材燒屍！<br />\n生為國人 何其有幸</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/08/132238_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F08%2F132238_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3a85dc47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">福氣來</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">生為國人 何其有幸 🙏<br />\n生為國人 何其有幸 🙏<br />\n生為國人 何其有幸 🙏<br />\n生為國人 何其有幸 🙏<br />\n生為國人 何其有幸 🙏<br />\n生為國人 何其有幸 🙏<br />\n生為國人 何其有幸 🙏<br />\n生為國人 何其有幸 🙏</span></span>"},{"pid":"2e15fce0fbcca4db641e9545df625b29708b4207","tid":837030,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T06:03:25.000Z","msg":"開名啦"},{"pid":"9fa720ec10eee0a268b69c2dff17e3972b3ec3eb","tid":837030,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T06:19:03.000Z","msg":"講野好浮誇好打手"},{"pid":"59f0c504d2ca88c9355be30a2fcd89b3546c3230","tid":837030,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T06:19:19.000Z","msg":"即係點樣進步左<br />\n佢試下大叫習近平下台睇下會點"},{"pid":"104ec5a09042351cf46e922b0ae15a49b250401b","tid":837030,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fa720ec10eee0a268b69c2dff17e3972b3ec3eb","tid":837030,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T06:19:03.000Z","msg":"講野好浮誇好打手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T06:20:45.000Z","msg":"跟本就係踩港毛"}]}